{"tid":1660593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(區議會選舉）選舉主任幾時先決定候選人有效","createTime":"2019-10-17T14:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:34:34.000Z","uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8aaa9588774320f5b54cdd2f7b10cb1a7e4326a","tid":1660593,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"今日係提名期最後一日<br />\n按選舉活動指引第3.25段<br />\n選舉主日要在提名期屆滿後14日內刊憲公佈有效候選人名單<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZqiBYR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZqiBYR.png&h=494c5c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但入咗閘又唔一定捱到選嗰日<br />\n因為魔鬼在細節，第3.33段留咗條尾，隨時都可以更改決定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMjOZcF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMjOZcF.png&h=53f634b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你，真係話DQ就DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而根據往績，垃圾會選到宣誓埋，都一樣可以DQ.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，個制度仲邊度信得過.....<br />\n<br />\n最後，循例補番句：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日街上見</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"97b36ad9021df4c227eb58d1478e8fd28c76da5f","tid":1660593,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4755081147230fc88ac001ecdf5f479d51c8349d","tid":1660593,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"5f5c5b3fb521848577674c42f8efc884d12cfa4c","tid":1660593,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:00:38.000Z","msg"